http://www.sbsc.org:80/discovery/bydesign.html 204.71.237.86 19970108134930 text/html 26036
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 13:49:43 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 08:31:03 GMT
Content-length: 25846
