<DOCNO>WT16-B18-76</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000254-B036-233</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/discovery/netcolum.html 204.71.237.86 19970108135312 text/html 7496
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 13:53:26 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 08:30:51 GMT
