<H3><CENTER><IMG SRC="image51.gif" WIDTH="147" HEIGHT="59" NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"0" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>
</H3>
<P><CENTER></CENTER>
</BODY>
</HTML>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT16-B18-110</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000254-B038-234</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/discovery/twntfrst.html 204.71.237.86 19970108135911 text/html 25285
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
